of 1992 by Sir Mark Weinberg and Mr Mike Wilson, former executives of Allied
Dunbar, brought in premium income of Pounds 101m in its first year.
New business figures for the group showed that total funds under management,
which are shared between J. Rothschild Investment Management, M&amp;G Investment
