<TEXT>
TODAY: Municipal elections in Bangladesh.
MONDAY: Provisional analysis of bank lending for house purchase (fourth
quarter). US construction spending (December). European Community foreign
ministers meet in Brussels (until February 2). European Community foreign
ministers also expected to meet Mr Shimon Peres, Israeli prime minister, for
follow-up to talks in December. Agenda includes review of 1975 co-operation
agreement, Israel's trade deficit with the European Community and future
European Community - Middle East relations. United Nations Human Rights
Commission begins six-week session in Geneva.
