equipment and furniture - showed no improvement at Pounds 2.17m in the six
months ended October 31 1992, against Pounds 2.19m, but profit rose from
Pounds 23,000 to Pounds 61,000.
Earnings per share were 0.59p (0.23p) but no interim dividend is being paid.
Previously it was 0.1p and represented the total for the year.
