FT  30 JAN 93 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
GOLD shares continued to perform strongly with the index rising another 29
to 904 for a gain of 11.7 per cent on the week. Vaal Reefs added R7.50 to
R162.50. Industrials put on 11 to 4,523 while the overall index rose 18 to
3,433.
